primary.context: Caller provided a recorded message instead of a request
primary.detail: The caller appears to be an automated system or recording that played a message back to the AI agent.

steps: User played a recorded message stating no one is available.
Agent attempted to collect a name but the call ended.

insights.summary: The call was answered by a recording or another automated system on the user's end, resulting in no request being made.
insights.verbatim: It seems like no one is available to take your call at the moment.
